## Explanation:

### Solution 01

- Here we can delete almost 1 character to make a valid palindrome.
- We took 2 pointers and iterates them from start and end.
- At any point, if we find the characters are not the same then we’ll pass the array with 2 pointers skipping one character.**`isPalindrome(s, i+1, j) || isPalindrome(s, i, j-1)`**
- This function will check it the rest array is palindrome or not.
- If any of these return true then return true.
- **Time complexity:** O(n).

